{"type": "article", "id": 21294, "title": "水果榨汁机", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-26T08:23:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115142y2SAH6q8FNOUdiJc.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t简易的榨汁机似乎依然是设计师的探索兴趣，外星人榨汁机常常被诟病华而不实，却依然是世界上最畅销的产品之一。而法国设计师 Serge Atallah 设计的榨汁器在处理水果的部件上与它类似，但下面变成了一个可以盛果汁的盘子。外面覆盖了一层滤网倾倒汁液并漏掉渣滓。榨汁机使用了 PMMA（亚克力）或 SAN 材料，可以打开滤网清洗，很方便。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150854JD8lXOBi32PfjrA7.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"717\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150854QBK3kxE6NpHPhygA.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"717\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150855T8KHhoOzWEdb5V9P.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"829\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.78952381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150856eNk9JEKvRA6hpcxq.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"690\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}